OL,3,GGrampian
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FIt will be another fine dry day
OL,6,Fwith plenty of sunshine with just a
OL,7,Flittle high cloud around in the
OL,8,Fafternoon. Very warm to hot inland
OL,9,Fwith some cooling sea breezes.
OL,10,
OL,11,CTonight:FA warm and sunny evening then
OL,12,Fa dry night with some clear spells,
OL,13,Fand a little cloud at times. Light
OL,14,Fwinds.
OL,15,
OL,16,CFriday:FA bright morning with some
OL,17,Fsunshine at times and becoming hot
OL,18,Fagain inland. Cloud increasing through
OL,19,Fthe afternoon with some heavy showers
OL,20,Fdeveloping, merging to longer spells
OL,21,Fof rain overnight.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
