OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Saturday to Monday:
OL,6,FSaturday cloudy and much cooler, some
OL,7,Fpatchy rain and mist. Cloudy start on
OL,8,FSunday then brightening up with sunny
OL,9,Fintervals. Monday dry and sunny and
OL,10,Fbecoming warmer.
